ConsumerNamespace.description: The consumer namespace for the asset. The possible values are: Industries

LicenseType.description: The license type for the asset. The possible values are: Aqs (Analytics Query Service) Cdp (Data Cloud) DataPipelineQuery (Data Pipeline Query) EinsteinAnalytics (CRM Analytics) MulesoftDataPath (Mulesoft DataPath) Sonic (Salesforce Data Pipelines) The default value is EinsteinAnalytics.
